== About ShortService
The ShortService gem is a layer for talking to the ShortService API (http://shortservice.lassebunk.dk), which makes it easy to shorten URLs with any service.

== Installing ShortService
$ sudo gem install shortservice

== Using ShortService
In your Ruby code, to shorten a URL:
  ShortService::Service.find_by_key("bitly").shorten("http://github.com")

To get a list of all services:
  ShortService::Service.all.each { |s| puts service.key + ": " + service.name}